author: neels
msg: *** Needs testing. Error reports and debugs welcome. ***
Enable summarizing diff for all working diff cases.
Completely replace summarizing diff implementation, preserving public API
signatures. Instead, implement summarizing diff by a set of diff callbacks.
(diff_summarize_baton_t): New baton type for summarizing diff callbacks.
based on svn_wc_diff_callbacks3_t for summarizing diff.
do_diff_summarize): New function diff_summarize_wc_wc, and replace the
other three. Copy diff_wc_wc(), diff_repos_repos(), diff_repos_wc()
and do_diff(), and remove the dependency on a callback baton of type
struct diff_cmd_baton, instead using the new diff_summarize_baton_t.
because we are now using svn_client__get_diff_editor() instead.
